{"tid":1471941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暴力？咩叫暴力？","createTime":"2019-08-14T11:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T12:51:56.000Z","uid":135445,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a8b68142d54bf09d552ed790356af0f249196f98","tid":1471941,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:58:14.000Z","msg":"狗二級燒傷都講得出 屌你老母 <br />\n講乜撚野話機場到私刑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有已核實身分的醫護人員聯絡本頻道，提供兩張荃灣被斬示威者（圖）送院時傷勢的照片。<br />\n<br />\n該名醫護呼籲，希望市民認清什麼才是真正的暴力，又稱不會指責昨晚在機場集會動手的示威者，因為兩個月以來不少示威者都被警察或者黑社會攻擊致受傷，而傷勢之重，與昨日於機場被打的疑似公安及環時記者根本無從比較，「好多人已經為呢件事付出好多，現在唔係指責或者割席嘅時候」。<br />\n<br />\n以下為傷勢照片，或會引起嚴重不安，查看前請務必做好心理準備。<br />\n<br />\n左腳傷勢：<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/z0k1UL0.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0k1UL0.jpg&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3eaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=a2e7484d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/z0k1UL0.jpg</a><br />\n右手傷勢：<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/oeH3751.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoeH3751.jpg&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3eaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=ea770e51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/oeH3751.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉自tg channel<br />\n依D就係赤祼祼既暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612faeb73743f19d52b82cd093efc9c30e6fd6dd","tid":1471941,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:59:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b77a55bb654c10fd4c2022af2272ad632a05f7d","tid":1471941,"uid":212119,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好係鏡頭做就得啦"},{"pid":"560ef777029cb4d626ff08c23efb426b9e9820a4","tid":1471941,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:00:33.000Z","msg":"Twitter戰線已開，擊退三毛洗板！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1471725/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1471725/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n幫推post然後10點上Twitter做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d2f136d1dc68c22f168396b7f566eb4297daca","tid":1471941,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd13f72a65afc0aa11700783326dd1cffe73c3e4","tid":1471941,"uid":263708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:00:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「重要！同我勁推」有高人教路如何找出popo前線鬼的痕跡<br />\n<br />\n睇下佢身份證簽發日期,因為popo係優先換證的。日期係由2018年12月27日至2019年3月30日。如係呢三個月,就九成九了。<br />\n如果隻鬼係打算長期混入去D團體度的,便例外。<br />\n如條友唔比身份證你睇,即係唔交心,更要小心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都是聽番來 不確定有冇用 希望幫到巴絲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">有人話比證件人看很危險 其實只需大家互看簽發日期一欄 其他資料遮住都可</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">我P牌開唔到新post今日 唔介意有巴絲copy開個專門post緊急宣傳比大家知道同研究</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"6861bd7da3beed93db81da6628167fa84d334129","tid":1471941,"uid":135445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:02:10.000Z","msg":"見到依D相有咩可能唔嬲大陸人呀<br />\n體諒下前線好冇呀"},{"pid":"daff3454d9d0b2bd335bcc8423999bdb6e3aa4a0","tid":1471941,"uid":198583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:03:08.000Z","msg":"俾人眼球都爆埋就唔暴力<br />\n<br />\n打條友兩槌就要生要死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24217ebaf24d9e63b08914a28c65f12d4352dfb4","tid":1471941,"uid":135445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"daff3454d9d0b2bd335bcc8423999bdb6e3aa4a0","tid":1471941,"uid":198583,"like":2,"dislik